{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents10OUDSButtonV","title":"OUDSButton","symbolKind":"struct","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}]},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/init(icon:accessibilityLabel:hierarchy:style:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/init(icon:text:hierarchy:style:action:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/init(text:hierarchy:style:action:)"],"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Enumerations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/Hierarchy","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/Style"],"anchor":"Enumerations"},{"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton\/View-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbutton"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout with text only, icon only or text with icon."}],"sections":[],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSButton","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Hierarchies","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Hierarchies"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Four hierarchies are proposed for all layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default (by default)","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Default buttons are used for actions which are not mandatory or essential for the user."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strong"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The Strong “call for action” on the page should be singular and prominent, limited to one per view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It should be reserved for the most critical action, such as “Next,” “Save,” “Submit,” etc.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"minimal"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Minimal buttons are commonly used for actions that are considered less crucial. They can be used independently or together with a strong button."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"negative"}]},{"text":": Negative buttons should be used sparingly to warn of a destructive action,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for example, delete or remove, typically resulting in the opening of a confirmation dialog.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A button with ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton.Hierarchy.Negative","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" hierarchy is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Icon only with default hierarchy","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), hierarchy: .default) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","    \/\/ Or simpler","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\")) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text only with negative hierarchy","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", hierarchy: .negative,  style: .default) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","    \/\/ Or simpler","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", hierarchy: .negative) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ A loading button","    OUDSButton(text: \"Delete\", style: .loading) { \/* the action to process *\/ }","","    \/\/ Text and icon with strong hierarchy","    OUDSButton(icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), text: \"Validate\", hierarchy: .strong) { \/* the action to process *\/ }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Styles","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Styles"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Two style are available:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default (by default)","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": used in the normal usage of button. The aspect of the button changes for following states disabled, pressed, hovered or normal (i.e. enabled)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"loading"}]},{"type":"text","text":": used after button was clicked and probably data are requested before navigate to a next screen or get updated data."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Colored-Surface","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Colored Surface"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If button is placed on colored surface using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"type":"text","text":", the default colors (content, background and border) are automatically adjusted to switch to monochrom."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Remark: Today it is not allowed to place a Negative button on a colored surface."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Specific-behavior","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Specific behavior"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For accessibility reasons, if the system settings for reducing motion is enabled, the loading indicator does not move."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For ecodesign reasons, if the device is in low power mode, the loading indicator does not move."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/48a788-button"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","name":"Version","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"2.0.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note"},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.10.0"}]}],"style":"note"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","title":"OUDSComponents","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It con